         <abstract id="aspace_2275c3ba7f699fe35cb73bde4e17dc51">Correspondence, financial and legal documents, maps, schedules, and newspaper clippings from the records of various Massachusetts railroads eventually incorporated by lease or merger into the Boston and Maine Railroad or the New York Central Railroad.</abstract>
    
      </did>
